name: Sarah Evans
description: I have a very fun-filled lifestyle and am always up for adventure. I’m looking for someone as down to earth and active as I am. I play basketball ,go to cinema,go to beach and enjoy traveling/exploring in the mountains every chance I get. I am very mindful of my health and am looking for someone with a similar mindset. I’m curious about where my food comes from, aware of what I put into my body, and am always striving to better myself. I do not eat processed, preservative laden, artificial “food”. I do eat wholesome, homemade meals most every night though i don’t enjoy to cook. It’s my dream to own enough land to grow all my own produce and have my own livestock. Kayaking, exploring new bars, restaurants, Mariner’s game, college soccer, fishing, hiking, camping, traveling, horseback riding, farming/gardening, ice skating, hockey, snowboarding..you name it. I’m game for mostly anything. I can buck hay, wrangle a pasture full of horses, bait a hook, gut a fish, and slip into a nice black dress for a night out on the town, all in one day. Originality goes far in my book. Woo me. There’s nothing sexier than a well spoken man who can sweep me off my feet. Please NO one word messages. Not a good first impression. Good chance I will not reply to something that can be sent to anyone.
